These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-1::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, aristoff, dunhill
1. the dunhill-smoker is on the left of the aristoff-smoker##1
2. the dunhill-smoker is between the alhambra-smoker and the aristoff-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |  2   |    3     |
| Cigar   | alhambra | dunhill | aristoff |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-2::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  security-guard, designer, firefighter
1. the security-guard is between the designer and the firefighter##2
2. the designer is on the right of the security-guard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |   3    |
| Job   | firefighter | security-guard | designer |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-3::.
